---
import ModuleLayout from '../../layouts/ModuleLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<ModuleLayout
  title="Reimbursement for Covered Costs"
  currentPath={`${base}/reimbursement/`}
  prev={{ href: `${base}/roles-and-responsibilities/`, label: 'Roles and Responsibilities' }}
>
  <section class="section section--intro">
    <p>SB 54 comes with real funding. Producers pay into a statewide system managed by CAA, and that money flows back out to support the organizations doing the work on the ground. One rule applies everywhere: funding covers new and additional work tied to SB 54 requirements. It does not reimburse what was already in place before the law took effect.</p>
  </section>

  <figure class="fpo fpo--filled">
    <img src={`${base}/fpo/6.png`} alt="Covered-material categories arranged as a clean circular still life — valuable commodities." />
  </figure>

  <div class="band band--tint-teal">
    <h2>Which part of the system do you work in?</h2>
    <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card__title">Local Programs</h3>
      <p class="card__description">
        For jurisdictions, Tribal governments, community partners, and haulers running local recycling programs or education and outreach activities.
      </p>
      <a href={`${base}/reimbursement/local-programs/`} class="card__cta sqs-block-button-element sqs-block-button-element--medium sqs-button-element--primary">See local program eligibility&nbsp;&rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card__title">Collection Systems</h3>
      <p class="card__description">
        For jurisdictions, haulers, and regional agencies improving collection systems and expanding service for covered materials.
      </p>
      <a href={`${base}/reimbursement/collection/`} class="card__cta sqs-block-button-element sqs-block-button-element--medium sqs-button-element--primary">Review collection eligibility&nbsp;&rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card__title">Processing and End Markets</h3>
      <p class="card__description">
        For Material Recovery Facilities (MRFs), processors, transfer stations, composting facilities, reuse hubs, and end markets improving recovery and material quality.
      </p>
      <a href={`${base}/reimbursement/processing/`} class="card__cta sqs-block-button-element sqs-block-button-element--medium sqs-button-element--primary">Review processing eligibility&nbsp;&rarr;</a>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="soft-egress">
    <p>Not sure yet? <a href="mailto:internalcomms@circularaction.org">Talk to CAA about your role&nbsp;&rarr;</a></p>
  </div>
</ModuleLayout>
